{"id":211481,"date":[{"year":1951,"month":1,"day":15}],"page":"7","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"文学界(2)","column":"","genre":"","count":"788","ytitle":"","mtitle":"十三国“和平”提案","ftitle":"","authors":["传志烈(1月22日7版更正为“张禹”)"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"传志烈(1月22日7版更正为“张禹”)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"‘他们所寻求的只有一件事情，乃是想获得一个喘息的时间，使败北的军队得以重加整顿，重新组组起来继续其武装干涉…。’"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——马立克在十三日联合国大会政治委员会的发言艾奇逊·奥斯汀的符咒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——‘友谊’、‘恩惠’…"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不灵了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杜鲁门的原子爆竹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"淋湿了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦克阿瑟的廿万‘精兵’"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"失败了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"失败了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦克阿瑟焦急不安"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啣着烟斗寂寞地踱来踱去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杜鲁门色厉内荏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在国会里干号"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天呀!或许美国少爷兵的长腿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能拯救自己吧?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"否则只有上帝才能保佑他们免于被"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歼灭……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(恰恰在这时候!)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们想起了“和平”处理朝鲜问题"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吓，和平吗?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和平神早已被非美委员会拘捕入狱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在英伦海峡又碰了一次壁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而在朝鲜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被成千成万的美国出品的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"‘长着翅膀的碎肉机器’杀伤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲜血淋淋……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然而他们确确实实想起‘和平’了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们也要‘和平’"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而且一本正经"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"由十三个国家的外交官提了出来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"编成为“议案”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那一班在昨天惊惶失措装聋作哑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"矢志否决"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中苏代表"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和平建议的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绅士们，——为‘和平’"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举起了他们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血污的手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫非发生了什么喜剧性事件了吗?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不，这一点也不希奇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当他们需要‘联合国’的时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们就把"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"联合国的旗帜撕下来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"插到麦克阿瑟的司令部和"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美制轰炸机"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坦克"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大炮上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此刻他们需要‘和平’了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们需要用‘和平’"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来阻挡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝鲜人民军"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国人民志愿军的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无情攻势"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝鲜游击队的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"广泛袭击"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——然后重新发动攻势"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(这有什么奇怪呢?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狼和蒋介石都曾经宣布‘和平’"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——当它被打伤了，还要"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"继续挨打的时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毒蛇也会化身为美女"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——为了便于吃人……)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可是，华尔街的杀人犯们:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这一切全然是白费"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花言巧语"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秘密武器"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"少爷兵加上美式装备"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上帝和走狗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"‘和平’等等"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全都经不起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鎚击"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是狼的病院"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是说漂亮话的华尔街走狗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(艾德礼、贝文之流的“社会主义”或者铁托的“民族主义”)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和平是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全世界"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们需要和平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了和平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战斗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到胜利!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五○十二，廿。上海"}]}